commit message:
Version 3.2.0 Update

This update also rearranges our current git folder structure to provide a lot more future flexibility for growth.

New 3.2.0 features:
- A wide array of bug fixes
- Moved to AppCompat from ABS
- Uped min SDK version to 10
- Moved to a Settings menu and added a ton of settings options
Rearranged the folder structure to simplify future builds
